title: Ratify the safe and signatories to be used for managing the Chiliagon DAO
body:
Members ratify by voting yes and making a token transfer of 0.01 MATIC to 0x1eB0487d99dC24B326faC3D63ADb913F88c8A542, that the following gnosis safe will be used for the purpose of treasury and grant management
https://polygon.gnosis-safe.io/app/#/safes/0x9526D8b5D98D7176AE04E3DFB996F56248f1AfE7
author: 0x51FcFc7D4A032478B8919e30cE52B39FbE823Fe8
